metadata.description: Complete GTO ranges with EV, frequencies, and 3bet scenarios for all 169 hands
metadata.source: Calculated from equity_6max.json matrix + GTO approximation
notes: EV values are estimated using: EV = (avgEquity - 0.5) * 8.0 + positionBonus
Position bonuses: BTN +0.20, CO +0.05, MP -0.05, UTG -0.15, SB -0.30, BB -0.10
Open frequencies based on EV thresholds for each position
VS3Bet strategies based on hand rank and average equity
